              A polyurethane suit and an afternoon of training is all
              that is between Ryan and a wall of fire as our Guinea Pig
              takes on the heat, but a twist of events sharply changes
              the outcome of his first experiment. Later, enclosed in a
              flashover chamber and engulfed in flames, Ryan has to rely
              on the firefighter's protective gear to keep his cool and
              hope the blaze is not too hot to handle.
